skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Get the latest news and headlines from the Free Republic website with the unofficial Free Republic News Feed! The user will get latest 3 stories from the website and the feed is updated every hour.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
